originalText.text: ZERO STARS!!!!STAY  AWAY FROM THIS PLACE!!!! THEY ARE THE WORST PLACE TO DO YOUR TAXES, I AM WARNING YOU!!! as a working young adult, I went into this place because a friend of mine worked at a daycare center and a child that attended there has family members that are employed  there and she recommended them. Not knowing any better, I did my taxes every year with them for about five years and was charged a whopping $400 because according to them you pay a fee that goes according to what you get back in taxes. I had two children at the time, so I was getting a good chunk back , of course I didn’t know any better. I paid that amount for five freaking years. Of course H&R Block also charges a very high amount but could you imagine if the tax preparer did this to every person with just 10 people alone she would be making a whopping $4000 imagine the more the merrier right! THEY ARE CROOKS WITH THEIR FEES!! THEY ARE DISGUSTING , DISGRACEFUL , AND WHAT THEY DO IS DISTURBING!!! THEY TAKE ADVANTAGE OF PEOPLE!!!! I CANT BELIEVE THEY ARE STILL IN BUSINESS!!!!
